<br>
Hound<br>
You<br>
<br>
Spider<br>
Pet<br>
<br>
Then run thru the spider and just past your pet and start hitting back off and attack with the hound targeted.  Try to hit back off right after the spider attacks the pet and if the hound hits you before the spider hits the pet he will switch.<br>
<br>
It is hard to do tho.  If run thru the pet from the other side you will be too close to the spider and it will hit you and mess it up.<br>
<br>
